    <h1>Doars Itinerary - 4 Days, 3 Nights</h1>







    <h2>Day 1: Arrival in Lataguri</h2>



    <p>Upon arrival in Lataguri, check-in at your hotel and take some time to rest. In the afternoon, visit the following attractions:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Lataguri Wildlife Sanctuary</strong> - Explore the sanctuary and enjoy a jungle safari.</li>



      <li><strong>Nature Interpretation Center</strong> - Learn about the local flora and fauna.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 2: Excursion to Jaldapara National Park</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, proceed to Jaldapara National Park. Enjoy a thrilling elephant safari to spot the famous one-horned rhinoceros and other wildlife. Later, visit:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>South Khayerbari Tiger Rescue Centre</strong> - Witness rescued tigers and leopards in a natural habitat.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel in Lataguri for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 3: Excursion to Buxa Tiger Reserve and Jayanti</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, proceed to Buxa Tiger Reserve. Enjoy a trek to Buxa Fort and explore the lush greenery. Later, visit:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Jayanti River</strong> - Relax by the scenic river and enjoy the serene environment.</li>



      <li><strong>Pukhri Lake</strong> - Visit the sacred lake surrounded by dense forests.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Return to your hotel in Lataguri for dinner and overnight stay.</p>







    <h2>Day 4: Departure from Lataguri</h2>



    <p>After breakfast, check-out from the hotel. If time permits, visit:</p>



    <ul>



      <li><strong>Chilapata Forest</strong> - Explore the dense forest and spot various wildlife species.</li>



    </ul>



    <p>Proceed to your onward journey.</p>







